lish <i>wacce</i>) + <i>horn</i> ‘horn’. Compare the discussion of   Wakeman  ."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["New Testament: ‘God is gracious’.  See  <b>John</b> ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When John Wakeman I was born in 1403, in Worcestershire, England, United Kingdom, his father, John Wakeman, was 23 and his mother, La Touche, was 198. He had at least 1 son. He died in 1437, in his hometown, at the age of 34."},"et":{"1403–1437":"1403–1437","1400–Male":"1400–Surnud","1435–1466":"1435–1466","1380–1460":"1380–1460","1205–Female":"1205–Surnud","1437":"1437","1403":"1403","1205":"1205","1435":"1435","1466":"1466","1400":"1400","1460":"1460","1380":"1380","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1403–1437":"1403–1437","1400–Male":"1400–Kuollut","1435–1466":"1435–1466","1380–1460":"1380–1460","1205–Female":"1205–Kuollut","1437":"1437","1403":"1403","1205":"1205","1435":"1435","1466":"1466","1400":"1400","1460":"1460","1380":"1380","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1403–1437":"1403–1437","1400–Male":"1400–Décédé","1435–1466":"1435–1466","1380–1460":"1380–1460","1205–Female":"1205–Décédée","1437":"1437","1403":"1403","1205":"1205","1435":"1435","1466":"1466","1400":"1400","1460":"1460","1380":"1380","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque John Wakeman I est né en 1403, à Worcestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, John Wakeman, avait 23 ans et sa mère, La Touche, avait 198 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1437, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 34 ans."},"de":{"1403–1437":"1403–1437","1400–Male":"1400–Verstorben","1435–1466":"1435–1466","1380–1460":"1380–1460","1205–Female":"1205–Verstorben","1437":"1437","1403":"1403","1205":"1205","1435":"1435","1466":"1466","1400":"1400","1460":"1460","1380":"